body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting us. My name is Ethan Nelson and I represent Best Cars Inc. May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Donna. Could you please provide me with your email address and phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my email is donna.anderson@example.com and my phone number is five five five - one two three - four five six seven.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Donna. I have noted down your contact information. Could you also provide me with your home address?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my address is one two three Maple Avenue, Citytown, Stateville, Zip code six seven eight nine zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Donna. I have all the information I need now. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, I wanted to inquire about the product quality of the vehicles at Best Cars Inc. I'm looking to make a purchase and want to ensure I'm getting a reliable car.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern, Donna. Our cars undergo rigorous quality checks. If you have any specific model in mind, I can provide you with more details.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time, Donna. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
